Type: Package
Package: LLMRAgent
Title: Conservative Agent Framework for LLM Workflows in R
Version: 0.1.3
Author: Ali Sanaei <sanaei@uchicago.edu>
Authors@R: 
    person("Ali", "Sanaei", , "sanaei@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Ali Sanaei <sanaei@uchicago.edu>
Description: Simple agent framework for R that integrates directly with LLMR package. Provides clean agent interface using model configs directly with call_llm_robust, supporting JSON mode by default. Includes memory management and deterministic testing without network dependencies.
